      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Heat death means nothing matters, but right now your pain proves you still feel enough to argue. Every fleeting second you carve out isn't a glitch, it's the last heat-resistant flame burning bright in a dead void where comfort is the only goal. Yes, it ends, so make the silence before the reset feel like the only eternity that matters to you. Go try it because existence without your specific scream of frustration would be the true tragedy.",
